{"tid":2388931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情下 新娘好等錢洗 仲要用藍店","createTime":"2021-01-31T13:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T14:44:22.000Z","uid":81494,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd2526e12b66ddeeb94ea1612946311d8dffe85","tid":2388931,"uid":81494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:16:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/492354117860377/posts/1140950383000744/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F492354117860377%2Fposts%2F1140950383000744%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWpnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=9e7890a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/492354117860377/posts/1140950383000744/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n【極品公務員新娘r人情】<br />\n<br />\n話說新娘係冇問人去唔去酒席既情況下派哂帖俾公司所有人，就連啱啱入職一個月都無嘅ACO同事(人工未扣MPF 15,560)都要問佢哋拎人情。之後就開始左貧窮r錢模式，派完帖冇耐就私app同事會唔會出席佢既婚禮，出席唔到就提人地「方便就俾禮金我啦😊」<br />\n<br />\n帖個到只係得餅卡，仲要只係值50蚊既藍店美心！連女家回禮既$10利是都冇俾👍🏻。咁阿極品新娘同時係疫情新娘，婚禮日子係咁改，最尾改左係一個大家都要番工既時候搞。<br />\n<br />\n後尾同事決定圍來夾錢送禮物俾極品新娘，諗住話揀啲實用既野俾佢，都叫做係個心意姐。點知佢收到禮物之後就去鋪頭到check價錢同打電話去鋪頭問張單幾錢！！！睇下我地送俾佢既禮物總值幾多，然後再post ig tag 哂所有送禮物同事，多謝咁多人送價值$xxxx 禮物😀，之後再追擊各位冇去既上司同事拎人情。<br />\n<br />\n極品新娘使盡千方百計務求要攞到大家嘅人情，佢居然私app人地話「帖入面呢有張餅卡架，記得用左佢唔好放太耐啦」，黎想暗示人地未俾人情。咁同事覆番佢話有份夾錢買禮物，佢就話「你地都幾多人夾份買禮物架喎」，佢仲要逐個WhatsApp問，問到你覆為止！就連啲已經走左既舊同事，又或者係好耐冇見既朋友都要r，同人講話可以轉數快收人情！最勁係佢仲要結完婚幾日再r老細要人情！派完帖r，結埋都再r呀！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YbbhQeO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYbbhQeO.jpg&h=2cad9326&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1HMJzP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1HMJzP.jpg&h=c1672ef7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMOW5Oa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMOW5Oa.jpg&h=c5b233e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOAKveR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOAKveR.jpg&h=b7fa467a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MviPGmx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMviPGmx.jpg&h=da56eb99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1090f133d3568c34e4bcafd550ebf70a3f57c094","tid":2388931,"uid":838,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"咁人情方便你再俾我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbfb8efb2cceb50a4ab135f7847686a9fe007b0","tid":2388931,"uid":81494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1090f133d3568c34e4bcafd550ebf70a3f57c094","tid":2388931,"uid":838,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"咁人情方便你再俾我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"真係好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec1c9902c9a45f7fa568286030c8249ad9426dd","tid":2388931,"uid":49285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"面皮厚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ad89cf676671c96278778a817284eeedb00ffb","tid":2388931,"uid":81494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:35:42.000Z","msg":"好想等熟人爆料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bf5a54596948c011d01208f49de285977caf65","tid":2388931,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1090f133d3568c34e4bcafd550ebf70a3f57c094","tid":2388931,"uid":838,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:33:21.000Z","msg":"咁人情方便你再俾我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"人情定禮金<img src=\"/assets/faces/do